_:Nc097c5d8d752479eb070cf89ae586763 <http://schema.org/description> "Details of the Council's members and register of interests." .
_:Nc097c5d8d752479eb070cf89ae586763 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The members are senior figures from the fields of science, engineering and technology. They are appointed by the Prime Minister, in line with guidance from the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://publicappointmentscommissioner.independent.gov.uk/regulating-appointments/governance-code/\">Office of the Commissioner for Public Appointments</a>. <abbr title=\"Council for Science and Technology\">CST</abbr> invites non-members to join sub-groups to advise on specific pieces of work.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"chairs\">Chairs</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/angela-mclean\">Professor Dame Angela McLean</a> <abbr title=\"Dame Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">DBE</abbr>, <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society\">FRS</abbr> - Government Chief Scientific Adviser</li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/lord-browne-of-madingley\">Lord Browne of Madingley</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society\">FRS</abbr>, <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> - Senior Advisor on Climate and Net Zero, General Atlantic; Chairman of the Francis Crick Institute; Fellow and former President of the Royal Academy of Engineering</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"members\">Members</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nuffield.ox.ac.uk/people/profiles/julia-black/\">Professor Julia Black</a> <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the British Academy\">FBA</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society of Arts\">FRSA</abbr> - Warden of Nuffield College, Oxford</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.otpp.com/en-ca/modals/bios/avid-larizadeh-duggan/\">Avid Larizadeh Duggan</a> <abbr title=\"Officer of the Order of the British Empire\">OBE</abbr> -  Senior Managing Director, Ontario Teachers’ Pension Plan, Teachers’ Venture Growth</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.mottmac.com/en-gb/about-us/people-listing-page/mark-enzer/\">Mark Enzer</a> <abbr title=\"Officer of the Order of the British Empire\">OBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Institution of Chemical Engineers\">FIChemE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Institution of Civil Engineers\">FICE</abbr> - Strategic Advisor, Mott MacDonald; Visiting Professor, University of Cambridge and Imperial College London</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.ceb.cam.ac.uk/directory/lynn-gladden\">Professor Dame Lynn Gladden</a> <abbr title=\"Dame Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">DBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society\">FRS</abbr> - Shell Professor of Chemical Engineering, University of Cambridge</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.eci.ox.ac.uk/person/professor-jim-hall\">Professor Jim Hall</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Institution of Civil Engineers\">FICE</abbr> - Professor of Climate and Environmental Risks, University of Oxford</li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/saul-klein\">Saul Klein</a> <abbr title=\"Officer of the Order of the British Empire\">OBE</abbr> - Co-founder and Managing Partner, Phoenix Court</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.century.tech/about-us/\">Priya Lakhani</a> <abbr title=\"Officer of the Order of the British Empire\">OBE</abbr> - Founder <abbr title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">CEO</abbr>, CENTURY-Tech</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://raeng.org.uk/about-us/who-we-are/staff-trustee-board-and-committees/president-of-the-royal-academy-of-engineering\">Sir John Lazar</a> <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> - President, Royal Academy of Engineering (ex-officio member)</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.stanford.edu/~nickm\">Professor (Emeritus) Nick McKeown</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> - Professor of Computer Science and Electrical Engineering, Stanford University</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://acmedsci.ac.uk/more/news/newpresident2024\">Professor Andrew Morris</a> <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society of Edinburgh\">FRSE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Academy of Medical Sciences\">FMedSci</abbr> – President, Academy of Medical Sciences (ex-officio member)</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://royalsociety.org/people/paul-nurse-12012/\">Sir Paul Nurse</a> OM CH <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Academy of Medical Sciences\">FMedSci</abbr> <abbr title=\"President of the Royal Society\">PRS</abbr> - President, Royal Society (ex-officio member)</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.jesus.ox.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/our-community/people/nigel-shadbolt/\">Professor Sir Nigel Shadbolt</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Society\">FRS</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the British Computer Society\">FBCS</abbr> - Professor of Computing Science at the University of Oxford; Principal of Jesus College, Oxford; Co-Founder and Chair of the Open Data Institute</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.manchester.ac.uk/about/news/new-vice-president-and-dean-appointed/\">Professor Sarah Sharples</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> <abbr title=\"Chartered Ergonomist &amp; Human Factors Specialist\">CErgHF</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Institution of Engineering and Technology\">FIET</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Institute of Ergonomics &amp; Human Factors\">FIEHF</abbr> - Vice President and Dean of the Faculty of Science and Engineering, University of Manchester</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.unilever.com/our-company/our-leadership/richard-slater/\">Richard Slater</a> - Chief <abbr title=\"Research &amp; Development\">R&amp;D</abbr> Officer, Unilever</li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.thebritishacademy.ac.uk/fellows/susan-smith-FBA/\">Professor Susan J Smith</a> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the British Academy\">FBA</abbr> - President, British Academy (ex-officio member)</li>\n  <li>Paul Taylor <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> <abbr title=\"Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering\">FREng</abbr> - Director, Morgan Stanley International</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>‘Ex-officio members’ are people who become members automatically because they hold a particular office.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"observers\">Observers</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/dave-smith\">Dr Dave Smith</a> - National Technology Adviser</li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alexandra-jones\">Alexandra Jones</a> - Director General, Science and Innovation at the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology (<abbr title=\"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\">DSIT</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jessica-glover\">Jessica Glover</a> - Director General, Growth and Productivity at <abbr title=\"Her Majesty's Treasury\">HM Treasury</abbr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"register-of-interests\">Register of interests</h2>\n\n<p>Members are required to declare any personal, political or business interests that could, or could be seen to, influence their judgement.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-of-members-interests--2\"><abbr title=\"Council for Science and Technology\">CST</abbr> register of members’ interests</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>" .
